</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="23.[151,1436,909,1129]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,664,948,974]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Field notes, habitats, and seasonality.</emphasis>
The 
<specimenCount box="[725,899,948,974]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" type="generic">two specimens</specimenCount>
were probably collected at night at a uv light trap when daytime conditions were sunny, dry, and mild as normal for this dry region of the Sierra 
<collectingRegion box="[1345,1435,987,1013]" country="United States of America" name="Nevada" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Nevada</collectingRegion>
mountains in September (R. Gordon, pers. comm.).
</paragraph>
